data.title: SAS Global Forum Proceedings 2018
data.text:
The papers published in these Proceedings document user-contributed presentations delivered at SAS Global Forum 2018. The presentations were selected by the SAS Global Forum 2018 Content Advisory Team, and these papers are published as submitted by their respective authors. Questions and comments about the papers should be directed to the authors.

The correct bibliographic citation for this publication is as follows: SAS Institute Inc. 2018. Proceedings of the SAS&reg Global Forum 2018 Conference. Cary, NC: SAS Institute Inc.
